properties.flavorText: With a thunderous roar, the sky dragon lets out a breath of lightning.
A rock formed by the nearby volcanic activity. It wouldn't taste very good in a sandwich, but it looks cool anyway.
A shiny, silver scale. It's not made of real silver, but it could probably pass if the market necessitated it.
A giant feather, with alternating black, white, and yellow barbs. These are commonly dropped upon the city of Vocalnus as the monster flies overhead.
A small coin covered in ash. You can barely make out the King of Frigri's face upon it. A little polish would do this coin well.
Please do something about that terrible dragon in the mountains!
